====Usage notes====
* ''Frei'' can mean “free of charge” only in the context of public services, e.g. ''freie Krankenversorgung'' ("free medical care"), and in some fixed expressions such as {{m|de|Freibier|t=free beer}} or {{m|de|freie Kost und Logis|t=free board and lodge}}. Otherwise,  {{m|de|kostenlos}} should be used.

